@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Create User
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "apiuser@test.com"
}

### Create Task for User 1 (Make sure ID matches the created user)
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Complete backend project",
  "userId": 1
}

### Get Tasks for User 1
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/1/tasks
